	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid agas, quomodo valeas, ignoro planissime.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fortassis ita occupatus in Sermonibus tuis emendas, ut vix ocium sit scalpendi aures.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nacto autem ocio velim paucis, quomodo valeas, significes.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Novi nihil habemus, et mirum, quod ex nundinis istis tam pauci libelli venerint prostentque.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l558" cert="high">Vitenbergenses</placeName> tacent, expectant fortassis meliorem ecclesiae <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxonicę</placeName> statum.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l284" cert="high">Lipsia</placeName> hęc audivi: "Aiunt comitia Caesaris fore <placeName type="citizen_name">Ertphordię</placeName>;; quę si fiant, actum erit de <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Magdeburgensibus</placeName> et <placeName ref="l61" cert="high">Bremensibus</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dux <placeName type="auto_name">Borussiae</placeName> etiam sibi timet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonię</placeName> puellam defuncto parente nobilem quandam duxit ac magnas sibi inimicitias apud suos conciliavit, quod regiam maiestatem adeo laeserit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name">Dantiscum</persName> atque alias quasdam civitates Caesar imperio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l425" cert="high">Romano</placeName> adiungere conatur, quę sunt regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonię</placeName>; unde bella horrenda iterum fore suspicor.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l302" cert="high">Lubecum</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l204" cert="high">Hamburgum</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1750" cert="high">Luneburgum</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name">Brunopolis</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Magdeburgum</placeName>, dux <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l743" cert="high">Pomeranię</placeName>, res <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l825" cert="high">Danus</placeName> atque alię quędam urbes evangelicę cum principibus quibusdam denuo conspirarunt se mori potius velle quam in Interim contra conscientiam consentire."</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc ille.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hiis diebus apud nos legatus a supremo magistro Teutonici ordinis fuit, qui ad regem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliarum</placeName> proficiscitur; habet pulcherrima dona, quibus regem honorare vult.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praecipue habet duo cochlearia mirabili arte effecta, lapidibus pretiosis ornata; puto ex osse nescio cuius animalis facta, quę vom habent contra omne venenum; unum regi, alterum reginę donabit.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid princeps iste venari velit apud regem fere divino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Item <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonus</placeName> quidam prima Maii apud me fuit, in quem forte fortuna incideram [in] <placeName type="citizen_name">Foro Piscatorum</placeName>, qui e <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l522" cert="high">Venetiis</placeName> venerat.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui magnam nobis spem fecit d[e...] evangelica doctrina in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Poloniam</placeName> suscipienda; nam regina bene vult evangelio et regem instigat contra episcopos quosdam, qui nihil minus ferre possunt quam Christi doctrinam.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> nondum accepit Interim.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Dissentit episcopus cum senatu,</foreign> eptit das sy iren predicanten und allen, die pfaffen sindt gsin, den eidt uffgeben, das sy alle alter und zierden uffrichten, wie sy vorhin gsin sindt; so wil er niemants geben noch zuͦ lassen ein kilch zuͦ predigen <foreign xml:lang="la">verbum domini;</foreign> er wils als haben.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vide illius <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18722">Erasmi</persName> ingenium tam vafrum et intoxicatum.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quis unquam credidisset hominem ex ista dignitate ita mutatum!</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileę</placeName> 7. Maii 1549 [1549].</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8171">Theodorum</persName> et <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicanum</persName> cum reliquis salutabis nomine meo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1278" cert="high">G[astius</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quę in <placeName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="l749">Saxonia</placeName> agant[ur] in hiis inclusis literis invenies, quas mihi remittes.</s>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Brevi catalogum librorum mittam etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Docto ac pio domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, Tigurinę ecclesiae pastori vigilantissimo.</s>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Go Zurich an meyster <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrich Bullinger</persName></s>
				</p>
			</div>
